text:
In last year's awards, Supergirl's Katie McGrath and Riverdale's won best breakout star, and the beauty of breakout star is that they're not nominated this year, so it's up to someone new to claim the title.

Tomorrow, prepare yourselves to vote for the best couple and sexiest moment! That poll will go live at noon PT, so keep an eye on @eonlineTV on Twitter.

You can already vote for best comedy and best drama, best drama acting, and best comedy acting, so don't forget to do that too!
